<p>
  
  
“The quality that we call beauty, 
however, must always grow 
from the realities of life, and our 
ancestors, forced to live in dark 
rooms, presently came to 
discover beauty in shadows, 
ultimately to guide shadows 
towards beauty's ends.”
  
